Patrón de código en <b>python</b> para {{c1::Alpha-Beta Pruning Search in Python}}:<br><pre><code class="language-python">def alphabeta(node, depth, alpha, beta, maximizing_player):
    if depth == 0 or len(node.children) == 0:
        return node.value

    if maximizing_player:
        val = -float('inf')
        for child in node.children:
            val = max(val, alphabeta(child, depth - 1, alpha, beta, False))
            alpha = max(alpha, val)
            if alpha >= beta:
                break  # Beta cut-off
        return val
    else:
        val = float('inf')
        for child in node.children:
            val = min(val, alphabeta(child, depth - 1, alpha, beta, True))
            beta = min(beta, val)
            if alpha >= beta:
                break  # Alpha cut-off
        return val</code></pre>

